title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Mar 10 2022

description:
Psaki on inflation, masks on planes. Peter Doocy to Psaki: Are you going to blame everything on Putin? Senator Ted Cruz joins Clay and Buck to talk about covid theater, inflation. He explains how Joe Biden caused the war in Ukraine, says we should give the Polish MiGs to Ukrainian pilots. C&B take calls to close out the day.
